sequenceDiagram
    actor Owner
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Owner->>Frontend: Confirm workspace deletion
    Frontend->>API: DELETE /api/workspaces/{id}
    API->>API: Validate JWT and owner permission
    API->>DB: Load workspace with channels
    DB-->>API: Workspace found
    API->>DB: Delete channel messages
    API->>DB: Delete channels
    API->>DB: Delete workspace
    DB-->>API: Deletion committed
    API-->>Frontend: 204 No Content
    Frontend->>Frontend: Remove workspace from local state
    Frontend-->>Owner: Refresh workspace selection
